            "The Exodus from Egypt - Since anyone who falsifies measurements is covering up their behaviour, making sure nobody will see them, and doesn't fear being seen by the Holy One. They thing that there is no divine supervision over human actions, and anybody who rejects this principle is like one who rejects the Exodus, since at that time divine supervision over us was made most manifest, with all the miracles and signs in Egypt."
